            </h5>
            <p class="text-muted">
              The library is being upgraded with new facilities for a better learning experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">
              Teacher Orientation
            </h5>
            <p class="text-muted">
              Welcome to our new faculty members! Orientation is scheduled this Friday at the Main Hall.
